{"tid":1160368,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"20年後再來看《醜陋的中國人》，事實比文字更具說服力~","createTime":"2019-05-18T12:10:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T16:19:47.000Z","uid":200120,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e44c9b6c8e78f6128b8157f0dec3fe5e0afd3028","tid":1160368,"uid":200120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T12:10:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/av52556831/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav52556831%2F&d=vM7vEUXlfhstYrouAjV2foGpPR2DWAUw81xbwDiv9SI%3D&h=d9a86f10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av52556831/</a><br />\n呢條片真係完美演繹何謂醜陋的中國人<br />\n第一個POINT,有民生基建就吹奏成國家對人民好,得撚啖笑,乜呢啲唔係國家嘅責任咩?<br />\n更何況起基建嘅目的係照顧人民?定為GDP GOGOGO? 就好似起一堆極少人流的地鐡站咁<br />\n<br />\n第二,無可否認中國人係有錢咗,送外賣真係可能搵到一萬蚊一個月,但個個都得?<br />\n嚟睇一睇真實數據: 全年全國居民人均可支配收入28228元，比上年增長8.7%，扣除價格因素，實際增長6.5%。<a href=\"http://www.stats.gov.cn/tjsj/zxfb/201902/t20190228_1651265.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stats.gov.cn%2Ftjsj%2Fzxfb%2F201902%2Ft20190228_1651265.html&d=vM7vEUXlfhstYrouAjV2foGpPR2DWAUw81xbwDiv9SI%3D&h=9d28c1cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.stats.gov.cn/tjsj/zxfb/201902/t20190228_1651265.html</a><br />\n即係月入約2352,真係得啖笑<br />\n<br />\n第三,以為美國驚中國科技實力超越自己所以打壓華為,但係華為真係有後門<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190401/59435871\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190401%2F59435871&d=vM7vEUXlfhstYrouAjV2foGpPR2DWAUw81xbwDiv9SI%3D&h=cef01b77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190401%2F59435871&h=111b0263\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190401/59435871</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/329890/%E8%8D%B7%E8%98%AD%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%88%B0%E7%95%A5%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E8%BC%95%E4%BF%A1%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%82%B3%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E7%95%B6%E5%B1%80%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%BE%8C%E9%96%80%E7%A8%8B%E5%BC%8F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F329890%2F%25E8%258D%25B7%25E8%2598%25AD%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2588%25B0%25E7%2595%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25BC%2595%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E5%2582%25B3%25E6%2583%2585%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25B1%2580%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%2596%2580%25E7%25A8%258B%25E5%25BC%258F&d=vM7vEUXlfhstYrouAjV2foGpPR2DWAUw81xbwDiv9SI%3D&h=87cf4a4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/329890/%E8%8D%B7%E8%98%AD%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%88%B0%E7%95%A5%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E8%BC%95%E4%BF%A1%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%82%B3%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E7%95%B6%E5%B1%80%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%BE%8C%E9%96%80%E7%A8%8B%E5%BC%8F</a><br />\n吓?完全當自己無辜,有撚病<br />\n<br />\n第四,以人民唔怕打仗當作軍事實力雄厚的根據,但無知都可以唔怕打仗,仲可以好似義和團咁練神功<br />\n<br />\n第五,係非洲搞基建係拉攏盟友,用經濟控制政治,唔通真係咁撚好心?仲係度沾沾自喜<br />\n<br />\n第六,以實行民主後產生的影響去批評西方民主,但至少民主動機係正確.最錯係將企業比喻做國家,企業打份工梗係冇權啦,ON99.最重要係民主社會可以一人一票去選決策者,例如代議民主制,喺效率同表達意見之間取一個平衡,而唔係有一個主席決定所有嘢,咁叫獨裁唔係叫民主.<br />\n<br />\n見到個TITLE真係好忍唔住要屌,成條片反映出大陸人真係好無知,仲有一班人真心或假意的人粉飾太平,20年完全冇進步過<br />\n<br />\n「我們的醜陋，是在於我們不知道自己的醜陋。」柏楊<br />\n20年後再來看《醜陋的中國人》，事實比文字更具說服力~<br />\n真係好可笑"},{"pid":"7bd935176555369b6c81bf7f6abfbf567dff5e3b","tid":1160368,"uid":200120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T12:11:35.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6e9f8cf4080efffd3251248545de9c1585aae714","tid":1160368,"uid":22422,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T12:13:23.000Z","msg":"我有一本<br />\n隨時拎嚟睇都回味無窮<img src=\"/assets/fac